	<p class="privacy-para">This Data Processing Addendum (“DPA”) forms part of the Master Subscription Agreement or other written or electronic agreement between Appy Pie (“AP”) and Customer for the purchase of online services (including associated AP offline or mobile components) from AP (identified either as “Services” or otherwise in the applicable agreement, and hereinafter defined as “Services”) (the “Agreement”) to reflect the parties’ agreement with regard to the Processing of Personal Data.</p>
