<p class="privacy-para"><b>5.2 SOC 1 Report.</b> Upon Customer’s written request no more frequently than once annually, Grobiz shall provide to Customer a copy of Grobiz’s the most recent service organization controls (SOC) 1 report for the Services. Grobiz may require Customer to sign a nondisclosure agreement reasonably acceptable to Grobiz before Grobiz provides a copy of such a report to Customer.</p>
